'''2013年科罗拉多州罢免选举'''是[[美國|美國]][[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]基层市民经过努力成功[[罢免选举|罢免]]两位[[科罗拉多州参议院|科罗拉多州参议员]]的选举。被罢免的分别是州参议院议长{{link-en|约翰·摩斯 (政治家)|John Morse (politician)|约翰·摩斯}}和州参议员{{link-en|安吉拉·吉隆|Angela Giron}}，两人都是[[民主党_(美国)|民主党人]]，支持严格的新[[槍枝管制|槍枝管制]]立法。起初有四位同类立场的参议员被提起罢免，但只有摩斯和吉隆的罢免选举获得了足够的签名支持。

请愿过程中，支持持枪权利和枪支管制的全国性团体都分别通过邮寄和捐款对双方提供支持。呈请书提交给州务卿后，摩斯和吉隆都向法庭提出了对呈请的质疑，但都被[[法官|法官]]否决。之后的一项法庭裁决导致选民必须亲自到投票站投票，不能再通过邮件进行；吉隆之后声称许多支持者因此没法投票而使他最终被罢免。最后，摩斯和吉隆都被其所在选区的选民罢免，这也是历史上首次有科罗拉多州议员被罢免。

==背景==
[[File:Colorado-Sen-John-Morse.jpg|thumb]]
2013年初，由于[[2012年奥罗拉枪击事件|2012年奥罗拉枪击事件]]和[[康涅狄格州|康涅狄格州]][[纽敦_(康涅狄格州)|纽敦]]的[[桑迪·胡克小学枪击案|桑迪·胡克小学枪击案]]影响，科罗拉多州议会通过了一系列枪支管制的法律<ref name="Los Angles - The Nation">{{cite news |last=Barabak |first=Mark Z. |title=The Nation; Gun laws trigger Colorado recall bid; The leader of the state Senate is facing an unprecedented effort to oust him. |newspaper=Los Angeles Times |date=2013-07-08 |page=5A}}</ref><ref name="Washington Time - Recall effort">{{cite news |last=Richardson |first=Valerie |title=Recall effort takes aim at Democrats after gun bills |newspaper=The Washington Times |date=2013-03-27 |page=A-3}}</ref><ref name="Denver Post - Gun-related">{{cite news |last=Bartels |first=Lynn |title=Gun-related recall efforts carry risks |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-04-05 |page=10A}}</ref>。新的法律中禁止销售装弹量超过15发的[[弹匣|弹匣]]，要对申请购买枪支的人进行普遍的背景调查，并且他们还需要为这一调查支付一定的费用<ref name="Los Angles - The Nation" /><ref name="Washington Time - Recall effort" /><ref name="Denver Post - Gun-related" />。起初请愿罢免的目标是州参议院议长约翰·摩斯和州众议员麦克·麦克劳克兰（{{lang|en|Mike McLachlan}}）<ref name="Washington Time - Recall effort" /><ref name="Denver Post - Gun-related" />，另外州参议员{{link-en|伊维·胡达克|Evie Hudak}}和安吉拉·吉隆也受到了罢免请愿<ref name="Denver Post - Focus now">{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Focus now on recall efforts |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-05-12 |page=1B}}</ref>，四人全部都是民主党人。

针对摩斯的罢免选举由基本自由防卫基金会（{{lang|en|Basic Freedom Defense Fund}}，简称{{lang|en|BFDF}}）和厄爾巴索縣自由防卫委员会牵头<ref name="Denver Post - Money flows">{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Money flows to both sides in recall effort |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-05-14 |page=4A}}</ref>，而针对吉隆的罢免选举则由普韋布洛自由和权利组织领导<ref name="Pueblo Chieftain - Gun group">{{cite news |last=Tucker |first=Jeff |title=Gun group moves to recall Giron |newspaper=The Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-04-12}}</ref>。

罢免请愿收集签名支持的过程中，支持摩斯的团体指控对方获取定罪罪犯的签名，并且收集个人信息<ref name="Denver Post - Money flows" />，而支持罢免的人们则称摩斯的团体在误导公众<ref name="Denver Post - Money flows" />。此外，这场罢免选举的支持和反对双方均获得了全国性团体的支持，[[美国全国步枪协会|美国全国步枪协会]]以邮寄和捐款支持罢免选举<ref name="Denver Post - Rarities">{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Rarities and recalls |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-05-19 |page=1B}}</ref>，而反对罢免的全国性团体包括{{link-en|美国投票|America Votes}}，据信还获得了[[纽约|纽约]][[市长|市长]][[迈克尔·布隆伯格|迈克尔·布隆伯格]]和[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]亿万富翁{{link-en|艾利·布罗德|Eli Broad}}的财政支持<ref name="Denver Post - Rarities" />。

==请愿的提交和认证==
[[File:Angela_Giron_2011.jpg|thumb]]
2013年6月3日，基本自由防卫基金会向{{link-en|科罗拉多州务卿|Secretary of State of Colorado}}，[[共和黨_(美國)|共和党人]]{{link-en|斯科特·盖斯勒|Scott Gessler}}提交了超过16000个签名请愿罢免摩斯，而只要有7178个签名就可以强制举行罢免选举<ref name="NY Times - Petitions submitted">{{cite news |title=Colorado: Petitions Submitted For Recall Vote |newspaper=The New York Times |date=2013-06-04 |page=14A}}</ref><ref name="Gazette - Gun-rights activists">{{cite news |last=Schrader |first=Megan |title=Gun-rights activists turn in signatures to recall Sen. John Morse |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-06-03}}</ref><ref name="Free Lance-Star - Perrotte column">{{cite news|last=Perrotte|first=Ken|title=Ken Perrotte column|newspaper=The Free Lance-Star (Fredericksburg, Virginia) |date=2013-06-13}}</ref>。同时有超过13000个签名要求罢免吉隆，只要有11285个就可以要求举行罢免选举<ref name="Free Lance-Star - Perrotte column" /><ref name="Deseret - 2d lawmaker">{{cite news |last=Wyatt |first=Kristen |title=2nd Colorado lawmaker could face recall over guns |newspaper=Deseret Morning News (Salt Lake City) |date=2013-06-10}}</ref>。罢免麦克劳克兰的请愿只收集到约8500个签名，没有达到所需要的10587个<ref name="AP - Attempt">{{cite news |title=Attempt to recall State Rep. McLachlan falls short |newspaper=The Associated Press State & Local Wire |date=2013-05-22}}</ref><ref name="Denver Post - Campaign">{{cite news|title=Recall campaign against Hudak is suspended |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-05-23 |page=2A}}</ref>，罢免胡达克的请愿也没有收集到所需要的18962个签名<ref name="Denver Post - Campaign" />。

一个支持摩斯的团体声称请愿中有50个签名是伪造的，其中一个姓名的主人两年前就去世了<ref name="Gazette - Fraud alleged">{{cite news |last=Noon |first=Alison |title=Fraud alleged in Morse recall campaign |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-06-28}}</ref>。对此基本自由防卫基金会的一位发言人立即发表声明要求展开调查，称任何在选举中舞弊的人应该要“以法律许可的最大限度”受到起诉<ref name="Gazette - Fraud alleged" />。要求罢免的团体声称摩斯的志愿者们对那些在请愿上签了名的人进行骚扰，要求他们删除自己的名字<ref name="Gazette - Harassment claims">{{cite news |last=Byrnes |first=Jesse |title=Harassment claims surface in Morse recall campaign |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-07-02}}</ref>。

===质疑===
罢免摩斯的签名提交州务卿并认证后，摩斯立即向请愿提出了质疑<ref name="CBS - June 18">{{cite news |last=Petersen |first=Barry |title=For June 18, 2013, CBS |newspaper=CBS Evening News |date=2013-06-18}}</ref>。摩斯的[[律师|律师]]马克·格鲁斯金（{{lang|en|Mark Grueskin}}）称请愿书都是有效的，但所有的签名均无效<ref name="WSJ - Key Gun-Control">{{cite news |last=Jones |first=Ashby |title=Key Gun-Control Backer Faces Recall in Colorado |newspaper=Wall Street Journal |date=2013-06-19}}</ref>。针对吉隆的罢免请愿也获得了认证<ref name="Gazette - Enough signatures">{{cite news |last=Schrader |first=Megan |title=Enough signatures valid for recall election against state Sen. Giron, officials say |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-06-24}}</ref>。两位参议员都声称这些请愿是无效的，因为其中没有使用州宪法中规定的明确用辞<ref name="Chieftain - Giron campaign">{{cite news |last=Roper |first=Peter |title=Giron campaign follows Morse's legal strategy |newspaper=The Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-06-27}}</ref>。州务卿主持了对两位参议员所提质疑的听证会<ref name="Denver Post - Attorneys Morse recall">{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Attorneys in Morse recall effort argue petition language |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-06-28 |page=6A}}</ref>，最终否决了这一质疑<ref>{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Petitions valid in Morse recall effort |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-07-04 |page=6A}}</ref>。

2013年7月9日，摩斯向丹佛地区法院发起诉讼，要求法院以[[禁制令|禁制令]]阻止罢免选举<ref name="Chieftain - Fight nears">{{cite news |last=Roper |first=Peter |title=Fight nears battle for votes |newspaper=The Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-07-10 |page=1A}}</ref>，与此同时州务卿盖斯勒也发起诉状，要求民主党[[州长|州长]][[約翰·希肯盧珀|約翰·希肯盧珀]]定下举行罢免选举的日期<ref name="Denver Post - Gessler hires">{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Gessler hires attorney to force Hickenlooper to set recall dates |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-07-16 |page=6A}}</ref>。2013年7月18日，丹佛地区法院[[法官|法官]]罗伯特·海耶特（{{lang|en|Robert Hyatt}}）在初步裁决中认定，即使摩斯和吉隆在法院对其进程提出质疑，罢免选举也必须进行<ref name="AP - Judge: Recalls">{{cite news |last=Moreno |first=Ivan |title=Judge: Recalls against Colo. senators must go on |newspaper=The Associated Press State & Local Wire |date=2013-07-18}}</ref>。希肯盧珀于是将罢免选举的日期定在9月10日<ref name="CNN - Colorado sets">{{cite news |last=Killough |first=Ashley |title=Colorado sets recall elections for two pro-gun control lawmakers |newspaper=CNN Wire |date=2013-07-19}}</ref>。

==选举==

===竞选===
选举日期定在9月10日后，枪击管控辩论双方的全国性团体开始较劲。美国全国步枪协会和{{link-en|繁荣美国|Americans for Prosperity}}支持持枪权，{{link-en|美国反对非法枪支市长协会|Mayors Against Illegal Guns}}和纽约市长迈克尔·布隆伯格则站在赞成管控枪支的一边<ref name="MSNBC - UP for August 4, 2013">{{cite news |last=Kornacki |first=Steve |title=UP for August 4, 2013 |newspaper=MSNBC |date=2013-08-04}}</ref>。莫斯开始挨家挨户上门努力争取选民支持<ref name="Gazette - Morse cross-hairs">{{cite news |last=Schrader |first=Megan |title=Morse, the man in the cross-hairs, campaigns door-to-door |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-08-14}}</ref>。竞选双方都指控对方抹黑自己<ref name="Gazette - Recall combatants">{{cite news |last=Schrader |first=Megan |title=Recall combatants spar over campaign ads |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-08-22 |page=6A}}</ref>。摩斯的支持者对一则指控他道德行为失范的[[广告|广告]]感到不安，指出在这些指控上摩斯都已经自证清白<ref name="Gazette - Recall combatants" />。吉隆的支持者被指称将问题歪曲成女性权利和堕胎上的选择<ref name="Gazette - Recall combatants" />。

财政捐款也同时跟进。布隆伯格捐出35万美元来支持摩斯和吉隆<ref name="HuffPost - Bloomberg donates">{{cite web |last=Siddiqui |first=Sabrina |title=Michael Bloomberg Donates $350,000 To Colorado Democrats Facing Recall Over Gun Vote |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/28/bloomberg-colorado-recall_n_3831029.html |publisher=Huffington Post |accessdate=2013-10-13 |date=2013-08-28 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053645/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/08/28/bloomberg-colorado-recall_n_3831029.html }}</ref>。加利福尼亚州亿万富翁艾利·布罗德也捐出了25万美元支持两位参议员<ref name="HuffPost - Bloomberg donates" />。民主党立法竞选委员会拿出了25万美元反对罢免<ref name="Wash Post - Gun debate">{{cite news |last=Wilson |first=Reid |title=Gun debate resonates in Colorado |newspaper=Washington Post |date=2013-08-29 |page=A03}}</ref>。美国全国步枪协会则花费了超过10.8万美元支持罢免选举<ref name="Wash Post - Gun debate" />。摩根和吉隆一方共计花费了约300万美元反对罢免，而罢免的支持者只用掉了约50万美元<ref name="Tribune - Recall ousts">{{cite news |last=Coffman |first=Keith |title=Recall ousts Colo. senator for gun control support \ Another targeted official reportedly trails in the vote |newspaper=Chicago Tribune |date=2013-09-11 |page=17C}}</ref>。

===替补人选===
罢免进程早期，乔治·里维拉（{{lang|en|George Rivera}}）宣布参选竞争吉隆的参议员席位<ref name="Chieftain - Rivera">{{cite news |last=Severance |first=Ryan |title=Republican to challenge for Giron's seat |newspaper=The Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-05-12}}</ref>。里维拉是共和党人，他原计划在2014年参加选举和吉隆争夺参议员席位，但在罢免进程中，他表示自己有意接替后者<ref name="Chieftain - Anatomy">{{cite news |last=Roper |first=Peter |title=Anatomy of a recall election |newspaper=The Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-06-09}}</ref>。里维拉需要获得1000个签名支持才能获得候选人资格，他于7月26日收集到了约1500个签名支持<ref name="AP - Rivera signatures">{{cite news |title=GOP candidate in recall race submits signatures |newspaper=The Associated Press State & Local Wire |date=2013-07-26}}</ref>。民主党人索尼娅·格雷特·温（{{lang|en|Sonia Negrete Winn}}）也有意争夺吉隆的议席<ref name="Denver Post - Union town">{{cite news |last=Bartels |first=Lynn |title=Union town not always unified on Dems |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-07-28 |page=4B}}</ref>，但未能获得足够多的签名支持<ref name="Chieftain - Ortiz appealing">{{cite news |last=Roper |first=Peter |title=Ortiz appealing ruling |newspaper=The Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-08-14}}</ref>。而在摩斯的选区里，州参议员{{link-en|伯尼·赫尔平|Bernie Herpin|小威廉·B·“伯尼”·赫尔平}}（{{lang|en|William B. "Bernie" Herpin, Jr.}}）宣布自己有意取代摩根担任州参议院议长，他也获得了足够多的签名支持而成为候选人<ref name="Denver Post - Hick">{{cite news |last=Bartels |first=Lynn |title=Hick seeks ruling from high court |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-08-27 |page=5A}}</ref>。

=== 法律争议 ===
2013年8月7日，[[自由党_(美国)|美国自由党]]发起诉状，声称因州法律和州宪法间存在冲突，他们无法让自己党派的[[候选人|候选人]]加入选举<ref name="Gazette - Ballots go out">{{cite news |last=Schrader |first=Megan |title=Colorado recall ballots go out as Libertarian Party tries to halt the process |newspaper=The Gazette (Colorado Springs, Colorado) |date=2013-08-09}}</ref>。州法律中规定候选人有10天时间收集支持自己成为候选人的签名，而州宪法中的相关规定则是15天<ref name="Gazette - Ballots go out" />。8月12日，科罗拉多地区法院法官罗伯特·麦加希（{{lang|en|Robert McGahey}}）在裁决中支持了州宪法的规定，自由党候选人可以到8月26日再提交他们的申请<ref name="Gazette - Ballots go out" />，{{link-en|科罗拉多州最高法院|Colorado Supreme Court}}拒绝受理[[上诉|上诉]]<ref name="Denver Post - Court ruling">{{cite news |last=Lee |first=Kurtis |title=Court lets recall ruling stand |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-08-16 |page=2A}}</ref>。这一裁决也意味着选举官员无法通过邮件来进行选举，选民必须亲自前来投票<ref name="Chieftain - Ortiz appealing" />。而摩斯则表示不能通过邮件投票“对大家都不利”<ref name="CBS Denver - Mail">{{cite news |title=Colorado Recall Without Mail Ballots Changes Dynamic |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053946/http://denver.cbslocal.com/2013/08/16/colorado-recall-without-mail-ballots-changes-dynamic/ |url=http://denver.cbslocal.com/2013/08/16/colorado-recall-without-mail-ballots-changes-dynamic/ |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=CBS Denver |date=2013-08-16 }}</ref>。

2013年8月27日，州长希肯盧珀请求科罗拉多州最高法院澄清，选民是否必须要先对罢免投票后才能对替补人选投票<ref name="Denver Post - Hick" />。与此同时，自由党人简·布鲁克斯递交了成为候选人的呈请书，竞争摩斯的职位，而民主党人理查德·安格朗德（{{lang|en|Richard Anglund}}）也宣布自己要竞选吉隆的职位<ref name="Denver Post - Hick" />。8月28日，州最高法院裁决两位参议员只有在多数票要求下才能被罢免，选民是否先对罢免投票与其之后对替补人选投票没有关系<ref name="Denver Post - Plot">{{cite news |last=Bartels |first=Lynn |title=High court, Bloomberg thicken plot |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2007-08-28 |page=4A}}</ref>。州务卿盖斯勒宣布布鲁克斯没有收集到足够的签名来成为候选人，所以只有共和党人赫尔平参加竞选<ref name="Denver Post - Plot" />。

