9月10日晚上，摩斯承认竞选失败<ref name="Tribune - Recall ousts" /><ref name="Wash Post - Colorado recall vote">{{cite news |last=Slevin |first=Colleen |title=In Colorado recall vote, state Senate president in a fight to keep his seat |newspaper=Washington Post |date=2013-09-11 |page=A07}}</ref>，最终的投票结果是9094票要求罢免摩斯，8751票反对，两者差距约为2%<ref name="Denver Post - Giron ousted">{{cite news |last=Bunch |first=Joey |title=Angela Giron ousted in Colorado recall election, thanks supporters in Pueblo |url=http://www.denverpost.com/breakingnews/ci_24064647/sen-giron-has-theoretical-advantage-going-into-recall |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921062628/http://www.denverpost.com/breakingnews/ci_24064647/sen-giron-has-theoretical-advantage-going-into-recall }}</ref>。原本进行的初步民调显示吉隆不会被罢免<ref name="Wash Post - Colorado recall vote" />，但实际上她还是被选民们以19355票支持，15201票反对的投票结果被赶下台，双方差距约为12%<ref name="Denver Post - Giron ousted" />。由于吉隆所在的选区中民主党人占47%，共和党只占23%，这个结果很让人意外，新闻记者报道称吉隆被这个结果惊呆了<ref name="Denver Post - Giron ousted" />。其它一些来源则声称吉隆仍然目空一切<ref name="Chieftain - Giron concedes">{{cite news |title=Giron concedes, joins Morse in recall defeat |url=http://www.chieftain.com/home/1831735-120/pueblo-recall-chieftain-com |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Pueblo Chieftain (Colorado) |date=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130921061548/http://www.chieftain.com/home/1831735-120/pueblo-recall-chieftain-com }}</ref>。吉隆还曾声称，这次罢免是因为许多选民无法前来投票，而《[[丹佛邮报|丹佛邮报]]》上有关不存在什么选民无法投票的说法纯粹是在胡说八道<ref name="Denver Post - Voter suppression">{{cite news |title=Voter suppression in Angela Giron recall? Hardly |url=http://www.denverpost.com/editorials/ci_24088344/voter-suppression-angela-giron-recall-hardly |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Denver Post |date=2013-09-13 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921062622/http://www.denverpost.com/editorials/ci_24088344/voter-suppression-angela-giron-recall-hardly }}</ref>。吉隆指出：“我们只有不到两个星期的时间，但还是不知道规矩是怎么样的。”她指的是投票方式从邮件改为亲自投票<ref name="Bloomberg - Voters to decide">{{cite news |last=Oldham |first=Jennifer |title=Colorado Voters to Decide Recall of Gun-Control Backers |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060430/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-10/colorado-voters-to-decide-historic-recall-of-gun-control-backers.html |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Bloomberg.com |date=2013-09-09 |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-10/colorado-voters-to-decide-historic-recall-of-gun-control-backers.html }}</ref>。

随着摩斯和吉隆被罢免，赫尔平与里维拉分别当选州参议员取代了两人的席位<ref name="CNN - Ousted">{{cite news |last=Killough |first=Ashley |title=Pro-gun control Democrats ousted in Colorado recall |newspaper=CNN Wire |date=2013-09-11}}</ref>。

==意义==
这是自1912年有关罢免选举的规定通过以来，该州首次有州议员被罢免。<ref name="Free Lance-Star - Perrotte column" />

===反响===
吉隆和[[民主党全国委员会|民主党全国委员会]]主席{{link-en|黛比·沃瑟曼·舒尔茨|Debbie Wasserman Schultz}}声称，吉隆被罢免是因为她的许多支持者无法前来投票<ref name="FoxNews - DNC head">{{cite news |title=DNC head Wasserman Schultz blames Colorado loss on 'voter suppression' |archivedate=2013-10-06 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2013/09/12/gop-calls-out-dems-over-accusation-voter-suppression-in-colorado-recall/ |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Fox News |date=2013-09-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006184611/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2013/09/12/gop-calls-out-dems-over-accusation-voter-suppression-in-colorado-recall/ }}</ref><ref name="MSNBC - Colorado recalls">{{cite news |last=Brockman |first=Jen |title=Colorado recalls are all about voter suppression, Dems say |url=http://tv.msnbc.com/2013/09/12/colorado-recalls-are-all-about-voter-suppression-dems-say/ |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=MSNBC |date=2013-09-12 |archive-date=2013-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914070314/http://tv.msnbc.com/2013/09/12/colorado-recalls-are-all-about-voter-suppression-dems-say/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《丹佛邮报》发表社论称该报虽然反对罢免，但很明显前来投票的人中反对吉隆的比支持她的要多，其中明显不存在什么选民无法投票的情况<ref name="Denver Post - Voter suppression" />。沃瑟曼·舒尔茨还表示，美国全国步枪协会和科赫兄弟所砸下的大笔金钱让民主党根本无法赢得这场选举<ref name="MSNBC - Colorado recalls" />，然而摩斯和吉隆所在选区中民主党选民的数量都要远超过对手党派数倍<ref name="Tribune - Recall ousts" />。科罗拉多州的最高级别民选官员盖斯勒则指出，前来投票的选民越多，民主党的表现就会越糟<ref name="FoxNews - DNC head" />。

一般来说偏向保守的媒体指出，两人被罢免的原因比金钱和枪支管制都要单纯得多。[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]和{{link-en|国家评论在线|National Review Online}}都称这是由于两位参议员忽视公众要求而引发的基层反抗<ref name="NRO - Famous Victory">{{cite news |last=Cooke |first=Charles C. W. |title=A Famous Victory in Colorado |url=http://www.nationalreview.com/article/358190/famous-victory-colorado-charles-c-w-cooke |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=National Review Online |date=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-09-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921055744/http://www.nationalreview.com/article/358190/famous-victory-colorado-charles-c-w-cooke }}</ref>。《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》把这次罢免视为美国全国步枪协会的一次重大胜利，也是布隆伯格市长一次“惨痛的失败”<ref name="WSJ - Gun-Rights">{{cite news |last=Jones |first=Ashby |title=Gun-Rights Supporters Score Big Win in Colorado Recalls |url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424127887323864604579069500613178582 |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Wall Street Journal |date=2013-09-11 |archivedate=2013-09-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930061332/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424127887323864604579069500613178582.html }}</ref>。

[[路透社|路透社]]称，这一失败表明，控制科罗拉多州政府的民主党已经做得太过份了，这不仅表现在枪击管控上，还包括其它方面，例如没有考虑同性收养的宗教豁免，以及同日选民登记等<ref name="Reuters - Arrogance">{{cite news |last=Coffman |first=Keith |title=Over-aggressive agenda may have doomed two recalled Colorado Democrats |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/12/us-usa-colorado-election-idUSBRE98B01620130912 |accessdate=2013-10-13 |newspaper=Reuters |date=2013-09-11 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924184640/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/12/us-usa-colorado-election-idUSBRE98B01620130912 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==再次试图罢免伊维·胡达克==
2013年10月4日，科罗拉多州务卿斯科特·盖斯勒批准了罢免州参议员伊维·胡达克的第二次呈请，罢免的支持者有60天时间收集至少18300个签名来在该州第19参议员选区强制举行罢免选举，这一选区包括[[阿瓦達_(科羅拉多州)|阿瓦達]]和[[威斯敏斯特_(科羅拉多州)|威斯敏斯特]]。<ref>{{cite news |last=Mitchell |first=David |title=Recall effort begins against state Sen. Evie Hudak |url=http://kdvr.com/2013/10/04/recall-effort-begins-against-state-sen-evie-hudak/ |accessdate=2013-10-13 |publisher=KDVR.com |date=2013-10-04 |archivedate=2013-10-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007022233/http://kdvr.com/2013/10/04/recall-effort-begins-against-state-sen-evie-hudak/ }}</ref>

